      "writtenOn": "2016-04-14T16:17:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Slirp defaults to calling slirp_init_dns_servers(NULL) in this case, which will get the list of system servers.\n\nNote that the ndns\u003d\u003ccount\u003e generation is moved to AndroidEmu in a future patch that also takes care of always setting the -dns-server in glue/main.cpp, i.e. before calling qemu_main() in vl-android.c",
      "parentUuid": "eb941ac3_fb1acfb3",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 3143,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 3145,
        "endChar": 5
      },
      "revId": "f82e37d46f109080786838ca9684bcd796279208",
